name: Echoes Of Existence 3
description: These will be a series of 1/1 variants that have all been manipulated by myself, the art changes but the theme is consistent, life finds itself often trapped in a void of miasmaic desire, what happens when one finally has enough? The soul caught in a yearning for more, a need to escape beyond the pale and ascend to a higher, more pure form of existence that creates instead of consumes. Join me as we explore the soul in various forms from the dissociative nightmares that accompany my bouts of depressive insight and into the world of sadness and beyond, let me show you what looks back into you when you find yourself having gazed too long into the abyss.
